GET     git clone https://github.com/hallwaykid/pw.git
INSTALL cd pw/ruby     # enter source dir
        bundle install # install dependencies
	./install      # link source to lib-path

        cd ..         # run in place, or symlink {css,js} to served path
USE     foreman start # HTTP and HTTPS on 80/443
NOTES
-httpd.ru can be used to launch other Rack-API servers ('thin' is default, unicorn works well)
-to allow listen on 80/443
 $ setcap cap_net_bind_service=+ep `which ruby`

HOST  mkdir domain/hostname
CLEAN rm -rf cache index
